      - When to use it.
      - Inputs / outputs.
      - Step-by-step outline.
      - Example prompts.
    - Add it to MODULE_REGISTRY and include it in MOVEON_PACK / EXPORT_PACK.

- Auto-Mode Builder (Meta-Evolution support)
  - Trigger:
