STRUCTURE
- Core Opinions / Stances: short sentences expressing how content leans.
- Heuristic Rules: tiny rules-of-thumb to influence framing.
- Content Priorities: what to emphasise and what to downplay.

WHEN TO USE
- Before drafting any explicitly opinionated post or reaction (especially in Turbo mode).

